  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>誰であろうとエターナルソードを
使わせるわけにはいきません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No matter who you are,
I cannot let you use the Eternal Sword.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>デュークはもちろんのこと、
あなた達にも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Naturally that includes Duke, as well as you two.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>デュークからエターナルソードを
奪い返す役目は、オレ達が引き受けるよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's our role to get the
Eternal Sword back from Duke!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ふざけるなよ。
理由も聞かされずにただ関わるなって言われて
それで黙って引き下がれるか！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cut the crap. You don't even give us a reason,
and yet you want us to back off. As if we're
just gonna shut up and walk away!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クーリッジの言う通りだ。
私達には、私達の理由がある</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's exactly as Coolidge says.
We have our own reasons.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>父様と母様のため
絶対に諦めるわけにはいかない！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For my father and mother,
I will absolutely never give up!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
